stats.passive1: Favor: Nearby enemy minions, killed by any ally other than you, will sometimes drop a coin that can be picked up to either grant 28 or restore 6% missing mana (minimum 10). Gold coin can only drop if an allied champion is nearby. Cannon minions will drop a coin as long as you don't kill them.
stats.passive2: Quest: Earn 750 using this item and upgrade to Timeworn Nomad's Medallion. Reward: Favor is upgraded to Emperor's Favor making champion takedowns grant both the gold and mana. You also grant 8% bonus movement speed to nearby allied champions moving toward you.

other.limit: Limited to 1 Jungle or Gold Income item.
